data.description: Come fall in love with this stunning one owner home. Looking for a home with no carpet well look no further. This modern home built in 2019 by Meritage in the master plan community of Sierra Vista can be all yours. This two-story home comes with 4 bedrooms 3 1/2 bathrooms a flex room on the first floor that can be used as a study or a mancave plus a Gameroom on the second floor. A Modern chandelier that fall from the second Floor into the foyer of the first floor. This home has high ceilings, modern ceiling fans and lighting, as well as a garden tub in the master bathroom. Book your showing today before this home is gone. This one won't last long and is move in ready.
